2015-02-22  Thien-Thi Nguyen  <ttn@gnuvola.org>

	Release: 2.39

2015-02-22  Thien-Thi Nguyen  <ttn@gnuvola.org>

	[int] Use ‘number->string’ more.

	* http.scm (msg-string-rcode!): ...here.

