	import SRFI 4 ‘make-u8vector’, ‘u8vector-set!’.
	(url-coding:decode w/u8vector): New proc.
	(url-coding:decode): Take optional arg ‘u8’; if
	non-‘#f’, arrange to return a u8vector instead of string.

