	(P chunked?): ...this new proc.
	(P handle-chunked): ...and this one.
	(P try-known): Delete proc, splitting into...
	(P known?): ...this new proc.
	(P handle-known): ...and this one.
	(P): Use new procs w/ ‘cond’.

